<DocsLayout frontmatter={frontmatter}>
  <h1>How Do I Define a Lifecycle?</h1>
  <p>
    Use a lifecycle when a capability has meaningful progression over time. A
    lifecycle names where work begins, which steps it can occupy, what it waits
    for, and what causes movement.
  </p>

  <h2>Make Movement Explicit</h2>
  <p>
    A transition should always say what caused it. Deadlines should cause an
    explicit outcome, and that outcome can then move the lifecycle.
  </p>

